ial group on a variety of&nbsp;transactions for both domestic and international clients.</p>','[{\"col1\":\"Lagos State University (LLB); 1990 \"},{\"col1\":\"The Nigerian Law School; 1991 \"},{\"col1\":\"The Washington College of Law (Masters in Law) \"},{\"col1\":\"He qualified as a Solicitor in England and Wales in 1999. \"}]','[{\"col1\":\"Intellectual Property \"},{\"col1\":\"Real Estate\"},{\"col1\":\"General Corporate \\/ Commercial Law\"}]','[{\"col1\":\"The International Trademark Association (INTA).\"}]',NULL,'[{\"col1\":\"\"}]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"id\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":0,\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"localeEnabled\":1,\"slug\":null,\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":null,\"dateUpdated\":null,\"root\":null,\"lft\":null,\"rgt\":null,\"level\":null,\"searchScore\":null,\"elementId\":0,\"metaType\":\"template\",\"metaPath\":\"\",\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"Person\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"\",\"seoTitle\":\"Wole Tejuoso\",\"seoDescription\":\"Wole Tejuoso is a partner at GBC. Wole has over 25 years experience of legal practice and is responsible for intellectual property matters at GBC Law.  He also focuses on real estate transactions and corporate commercial law.\",\"seoKeywords\":\"gbenga biobaku & co, gbc, law, nigeria, wole, Tejuoso, legal practice, corporate, commercial, Sheikh & Co. Solicitors, INTA, Intellectual Property, Real Estate, General Corporate\\/Commercial Law\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"summary\",\"openGraphType\":\"website\",\"robots\":\"\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageId\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageId\":\"\",\"seoTitleUnparsed\":\"Wole Tejuoso\",\"seoDescriptionUnparsed\":\"Wole Tejuoso is a partner at GBC. Wole has over 25 years experience of legal practice and is responsible for intellectual property matters at GBC Law.  He also focuses on real estate transactions and corporate commercial law.\",\"s