ce, renewal of Oil Prospecting Licenses (OPLs) and Oil Mining Lease (OMLs), and commercial transactions and projects.\"},{\"col1\":\"Provided drafting and legislative support to the Technical Team advising the National Assembly on the Petroleum Industry Reform Bills.\"},{\"col1\":\"Acted as member of the team of solicitors that represented Niger State in the structuring and negotiation of a Public Private Partnership (PPP) arrangement for the Minna\\/Suleja Water Concession Project.\"},{\"col1\":\"Acted as member of the Technical Committee that drafted the Administration of Criminal Justice Bill for Kaduna State.\"}]','[{\"col1\":\"\"}]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"id\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":0,\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"localeEnabled\":1,\"slug\":null,\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":null,\"dateUpdated\":null,\"root\":null,\"lft\":null,\"rgt\":null,\"level\":null,\"searchScore\":null,\"elementId\":0,\"metaType\":\"template\",\"metaPath\":\"\",\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitle\":\"Joseph Omoba\",\"seoDescription\":\"A modern law firm with a flair for business\",\"seoKeywords\":\"gbenga biobaku & co, gbc, law, nigeria, oil and gas, litigation, general corporate commercial, business advisory\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"summary\",\"openGraphType\":\"website\",\"robots\":\"\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageId\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageId\":\"\",\"seoTitleUnparsed\":\"Joseph Omoba\",\"seoDescriptionUnparsed\":\"A modern law firm with a flair for business\",\"seoKeywordsUnparsed\":\"gbenga biobaku & co, gbc, law, nigeria, oil and gas, litigation, general corporate commercial, business advisory\",\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceFiel