oma’s area of practice and expertise includes Company Secretarial, Business Advisory and Regulatory matters, Immigration Law and Intellectual Property Law.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p> We are confident that this attainment would further strengthen and deepen our Firm’s capability in providing top notch quality services to our clients.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p> Congratulations Ijeoma!</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p><strong>Our Partner/ Director Administration Inducted into the Institute of Chartered Secretaries of Nigeria (ICSAN)</strong></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"id\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":0,\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"localeEnabled\":1,\"slug\":null,\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":null,\"dateUpdated\":null,\"root\":null,\"lft\":null,\"rgt\":null,\"level\":null,\"searchScore\":null,\"elementId\":0,\"metaType\":\"template\",\"metaPath\":\"\",\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"CreativeWork\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"WebPage\",\"seoTitle\":\"ANOTHER FEATHER IN HER CAP\",\"seoDescription\":\"A modern law firm with a flair for business\",\"seoKeywords\":\"gbenga biobaku & co, gbc, law, nigeria, oil and gas, litigation, general corporate commercial, business advisory\",\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"summary\",\"openGraphType\":\"website\",\"robots\":\"\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"seoTwitterImageId\":\"\",\"seoFacebookImageId\":\"\",\"seoTitleUnparsed\":\"Another feather in her cap\",\"seoDescriptionUnparsed\":\"A modern law firm with a flair for business\",\"seoKeywordsUnparsed\":\"gbenga biobaku & co, gbc, law, nigeria, oil and gas, litigation, general corporate commercial, business advisory\",\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"