es worth $15 million USD.\"},{\"col1\":\"Acted for a land drilling company in an $18 million private equity investment.\"},{\"col1\":\"Advised and assistd several clients on the establishment of Nigerian subsidiaries and procuring relevant pre-investment and operational approvals, licenses and permits.\"}]','[{\"col1\":\"\"}]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"seoMainEntityCategory\":\"Person\",\"seoMainEntityOfPage\":\"\",\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoTitleUnparsed\":\"Ijeoma Abalogu\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescriptionUnparsed\":\"Ijeoma Abalogu is a Senior Associate at GBC. Ijeoma heads the Firm’s Business Advisory and Company Secretarial unit. She has over 11 years practice experience and has advised several companies on the establishment of business entities in Nigeria, as well as completed registration and obtaining relevant licenses and approvals for corporate clients including Statoil, Baker Hughes, Parker Drilling, Vmonitor and several other companies.\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywordsUnparsed\":\"gbenga biobaku & co, gbc, law, nigeria, oil and gas, corporate and commercial law, legal advisory, regulatory compliance, intellectual property, business startups, international investments, private equity\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"field\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"image\",\"seoImageId\":[\"50\"],\"seoImageTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"summary\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSource\":\"field\",\"seoTwitterImageIdSourceField\":\"image\",\"seoTwitterImageId\":[\"50\"],\"seoTwitterImageTransform\":\"\",\"openGraphType\":\"website\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSource\":\"field\",\"seoFacebookImageIdSourceField\":\"image\",\"seoFacebookImageId\":[\"50\"],\"seoFacebookImageTransform\":\"\",\"robots\":\"\"}','2020-11-24 16:37:24','2020-11-24 16:37:24','cb847e20-3505-422a-bc94-af46f72a85fb'),(264,374,1,' F